CREATE TABLE fields (field_id INT PRIMARY KEY, field_name VARCHAR(50), field_size FLOAT, crop_id INT REFERENCES crops(crop_id))

CREATE TABLE farmers (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, location VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE fields (field_id INT PRIMARY KEY, field_name VARCHAR(50), field_size FLOAT, crop_id INT REFERENCES crops(crop_id))

CREATE TABLE harvest (harvest_id INT PRIMARY KEY, harvest_date DATE, quantity INT, crop_id INT REFERENCES crops(crop_id))</t><s>insert into crops (crop_id, crop_name, crop_type, farmer_id) select 1, 'corn', 'grain', 1</s>

<t>CREATE TABLE farmers (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, location VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE crops (crop_id INT PRIMARY KEY, crop_name VARCHAR(50), crop_type VARCHAR(50), farmer_id INT REFERENCES farmers(id))

CREATE TABLE harvest (harvest_id INT PRIMARY KEY, harvest_date DATE, quantity INT, crop_id INT REFERENCES crops(crop_id))

CREATE TABLE fields (field_id INT PRIMARY KEY, field_name VARCHAR(50), field_size FLOAT, crop_id INT REFERENCES crops(crop_id))</t><s>INSERT INTO crops (crop_id, crop_name, crop_type, farmer_id) SELECT 3, 'Rice', 'Grain', 3</s>

CREATE TABLE crops (crop_id INT PRIMARY KEY, crop_name VARCHAR(50), crop_type VARCHAR(50), farmer_id INT REFERENCES farmers(id))</t><s>INSERT INTO crops (crop_id, crop_name, crop_type, farmer_id) SELECT 4, 'Soybeans', 'Legume', 4</s>

CREATE TABLE crops (crop_id INT PRIMARY KEY, crop_name VARCHAR(50), crop_type VARCHAR(50), farmer_id INT REFERENCES farmers(id))

CREATE TABLE harvest (harvest_id INT PRIMARY KEY, harvest_date DATE, quantity INT, crop_id INT REFERENCES crops(crop_id))</t><s>insert into fields (field_id, field_name, field_size, crop_id) select 5, 'field 5', 12.0, 5</s>

<t>CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>INSERT INTO farm (id, name, location, established_date) SELECT 1, 'Farm 1', 'Location 1', '2022-01-01'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)</t><s>INSERT INTO farm (id, name, location, established_date) SELECT 1, 'Farm 1', 'Location 1', '2022-01-01'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>insert into crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) select 1, 'crop 1', 'vegetable', 'spring', 100.5</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>INSERT INTO crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) SELECT 1, 'Crop 1', 'Vegetable', 'Spring', 100.5</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>insert into crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) select 1, 'crop 1', 'vegetable', 'spring', 100.5</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

<t>CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)</t><s>insert into crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) select 1, 'crop 1', 'vegetable', 'spring', 100.5</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>insert into farmer (id, name, age, gender, phone_number) select 1, 'john doe', 30, 'male', '123-456-7890'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)</t><s>insert into field (id, farm_id, size, soil_type) select 1, 1, 10.5, 'clay'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>insert into field (id, farm_id, size, soil_type) select 1, 1, 10.5, 'clay'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)</t><s>insert into field (id, farm_id, size, soil_type) select 1, 1, 10.5, 'clay'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>insert into machinery (id, name, type, condition) select 1, 'tractor 1', 'tractor', 'good'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)</t><s>insert into machinery (id, name, type, condition) select 1, 'tractor 1', 'tractor', 'good'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>insert into farm (id, name, location, established_date) select 2, 'farm 2', 'location 2', '2022-02-01'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>insert into farm (id, name, location, established_date) select 2, 'farm 2', 'location 2', '2022-02-01'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))</t><s>insert into farm (id, name, location, established_date) select 2, 'farm 2', 'location 2', '2022-02-01'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))</t><s>insert into crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) select 2, 'crop 2', 'fruit', 'summer', 150.7</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>INSERT INTO crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) SELECT 2, 'Crop 2', 'Fruit', 'Summer', 150.7</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>insert into crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) select 2, 'crop 2', 'fruit', 'summer', 150.7</s>

<t>CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)</t><s>INSERT INTO crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) SELECT 2, 'Crop 2', 'Fruit', 'Summer', 150.7</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>insert into farmer (id, name, age, gender, phone_number) select 2, 'jane smith', 25, 'female', '987-654-3210'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>INSERT INTO farmer (id, name, age, gender, phone_number) SELECT 2, 'Jane Smith', 25, 'Female', '987-654-3210'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

<t>CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>insert into field (id, farm_id, size, soil_type) select 2, 2, 15.7, 'sandy loam'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>INSERT INTO machinery (id, name, type, condition) SELECT 2, 'Harvester 1', 'Harvester', 'Fair'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)</t><s>INSERT INTO machinery (id, name, type, condition) SELECT 2, 'Harvester 1', 'Harvester', 'Fair'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))</t><s>INSERT INTO farm (id, name, location, established_date) SELECT 3, 'Farm 3', 'Location 3', '2022-03-01'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)</t><s>insert into farm (id, name, location, established_date) select 3, 'farm 3', 'location 3', '2022-03-01'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>INSERT INTO crop (id, name, type, growing_season, yield_per_acre) SELECT 3, 'Crop 3', 'Grain', 'Fall', 200.2</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)</t><s>INSERT INTO farmer (id, name, age, gender, phone_number) SELECT 3, 'Mike Johnson', 35, 'Male', '555-123-4567'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))</t><s>INSERT INTO farmer (id, name, age, gender, phone_number) SELECT 3, 'Mike Johnson', 35, 'Male', '555-123-4567'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS crop (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), growing_season VARCHAR(50), yield_per_acre FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)</t><s>insert into farmer (id, name, age, gender, phone_number) select 3, 'mike johnson', 35, 'male', '555-123-4567'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>INSERT INTO field (id, farm_id, size, soil_type) SELECT 3, 3, 20.2, 'Loamy Sand'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS machinery (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), type VARCHAR(50), condition VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farmer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, gender VARCHAR(10), phone_number VARCHAR(15))</t><s>INSERT INTO field (id, farm_id, size, soil_type) SELECT 3, 3, 20.2, 'Loamy Sand'</s>

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS farm (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), location VARCHAR(100), established_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS field (id INT PRIMARY KEY, farm_id INT, size FLOAT, soil_type VARCHAR(50), FOREIGN KEY (farm_id) REFERENCES farm(id) ON DELETE CASCADE)</t><s>INSERT INTO field (id, farm_id, size, soil_type) SELECT 3, 3, 20.2, 'Loamy Sand'</s>
